$interpreted: Sharice: Angel, a little to the left...
Sharice: okay. Keep moving forward.
Sharice: Good. Alright, go!
Angelia: Yay! Got it!
Naya: It's been so long since I've seen Angel so relaxed.
Sione: Dragging her out here to play for a few days was definitely the right decision.
Puggi: Stunning Sharice〜Miss Naya〜Sumptuous Sione〜Angelia the Angel, look over here〜
Sharice: Puggi, go play somewhere else, don't bother us!
Angelia: Sharice, is it okay for Puggi to have that device?
Sharice: Whatever. Don't know what that is anyway. Plus, if we give it to him to play with, it's better than him coming here and harassing us.
Puggi: Miss Naya, what a figure~
Naya: Stinky, dirty bird, what are you looking at!?
Naya: Got it. Let's go over there and rest a bit!
Angelia: *whew*~These few days have been so fun.
Angelia: Sharice, thanks for bringing these toys to use in the water. When we get back to the Kingdom, you've got to remember to send your family my thanks.
Sharice: Oh...when I send them a letter I'll be sure to bring it up.
Angelia: Letter? You still have several days off. Don't you plan on going home for a bit?
Sione: I've heard you don't like to take too long of a vacation. You just stay at the barracks. Is something the matter?
Sharice: Actually, I got in a big argument with my family over some things. That's why I entered the army...
Angelia: Argument?
Sharice: Before, I was the only child in my family. After my younger brother was born, my parents only cared about my brother and paid no attention to me.
Sharice: So I left home and went to the army. I thought I just needed to become stronger and then my family would accept me.
Sione: But you still have letters coming in. Seems like your relationship is not that bad.
Sharice: After I helped my brother find a medicine that helped him our relationship improved a bit.
Sharice: But they don't want me to come home and they won't come see me in the army. They just see what I've mentioned in my letters and send it over.
Sharice: Feels like they're paying me back for saving their beloved son...
Naya: ...Why is everyone looking so down in the dumps?
Naya: Oh, yea. I just found the instruction manual for that Rune item.
Naya: It was probably because of those Aqua Wolves that this instruction manual got all crumpled in a ball and tossed near the luggage.
Angelia: So what's the function of the item?
Naya: Let me see..."Image Recording Device by the Carterwells".
Naya: When the item is flashing, it will record an image of that moment in time. Then it will reproduce it on a piece of paper. Like a simulation of a real image.
Naya: Wha! In the back is a message from Sharice's family!
Naya: "Sharice, after your brother was born we overlooked how it made you feel.
Naya: So we understand why you are mad and why you don't want to come home.
Angelia: We hope you can at least use this device to record some of your daily life and send the pictures home.
Angelia: That way, even though you don't come see us, we can know how you're doing and can use it to think of you..."
Angelia: If they didn't care about you and only wanted to pay you back, they wouldn't use this in order to think of you. Don't you think?
Sione: They're thinking of you, but they just don't know how to say it. That's family for you. Nobody knows how to express their feelings.
Angelia: This is their way of expressing their love.
Sharice: ...Since it's like that, I guess I should find the time to make it home.
Naya: Haha! Isn't it great to have this kind of an ending?
Sione: Wait a second! That's not right!
Sione: If this Rune item can record images...then what has Puggi been doing flashing it at us for all this time...?
Angelia: What we are wearing has been recorded!?
Naya: Ahhh!!! That stinky chicken has been flashing that at our butts the whole time!
Angelia: And I chose the most transparent swimsuit...
Sharice: If people see me like this, how am I going to return home!
Sione: Let's get Puggi and take that device back!
Angelia: Everybody, change back into your clothes!!
